October 31, 2019
On Thursday, October 31, 2019, the President signed into law:S. 1196, which designates a facility of the United States Postal Service located at 1715 Linnerud Drive in Sun Prairie, Wisconsin, as the Fire Captain Cory Barr Post Office Building.
